                                                                    <div
                                                                        style="box-sizing:border-box; text-align:justify; font-family:Muli, sans-serif; font-size:16px; color:#000000; line-height:1.6;">
                                                                        <p style="margin-top:0; margin-bottom:1em;">
                                                                            Enterprise programs running on <strong>MS
                                                                                Dynamics 365 Operations</strong> are
                                                                            subject to frequent changes &ndash;
                                                                            customizations, integrations, regulatory
                                                                            updates, and platform releases. Without a
                                                                            structured and scalable testing approach,
                                                                            these changes can introduce production
                                                                            risks, operational disruptions, and
                                                                            increased cost of quality.</p>
                                                                        <p style="margin-top:0; margin-bottom:1em;">Our
                                                                            <strong>Testing-as-a-Service (TaaS) for
                                                                                Dynamics 365 Operations</strong> is
                                                                            designed to provide <strong>continuous
                                                                                validation across change, release, and
                                                                                run cycles</strong>, ensuring every
                                                                            deployment is production-ready, compliant,
                                                                            and business-aligned.</p>
                                                                        <h2
                                                                            style="font-size:22px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.8em; margin-bottom:0.8em;">
                                                                            Why Testing is Critical for Dynamics 365
                                                                            Operations</h2>
                                                                        <p style="margin-bottom:1em;">Dynamics 365
                                                                            Operations environments are complex by
                                                                            design. Typical challenges include:</p>
                                                                        <ul
                                                                            style="margin-bottom:1em; padding-left:1.5em; color:#000000; font-family:Muli, sans-serif; font-size:16px;">
                                                                            <li>Frequent configuration and customization
                                                                                changes</li>
                                                                            <li>Multiple integrations with upstream and
                                                                                downstream systems</li>
                                                                            <li>Regular platform and application
                                                                                releases</li>
                                                                            <li>Business-critical batch jobs and data
                                                                                processes</li>
                                                                            <li>High dependency on role-based security
                                                                                and workflows</li>
                                                                        </ul>
                                                                        <p style="margin-bottom:1em;">A traditional,
                                                                            one-time testing approach is no longer
                                                                            sufficient. Enterprises need a
                                                                            <strong>repeatable, reusable, and
                                                                                governance-driven testing model</strong>
                                                                            that scales with change velocity.</p>
                                                                        <h2
                                                                            style="font-size:22px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.8em; margin-bottom:0.8em;">
                                                                            Dynamics 365 Operations Test Assets &amp;
                                                                            Accelerators</h2>
                                                                        <p style="margin-bottom:1em;">To reduce
                                                                            onboarding time and improve efficiency, our
                                                                            TaaS model leverages <strong>pre-built and
                                                                                reusable testing assets</strong>.</p>
                                                                        <h3
                                                                            style="font-size:18px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.6em; margin-bottom:0.6em;">
                                                                            Jump-Start Testing Packages</h3>
                                                                        <p style="margin-bottom:0.8em;">Designed to
                                                                            quickly stabilize testing for new or
                                                                            transitioning programs:</p>
                                                                        <ul
                                                                            style="margin-bottom:1em; padding-left:1.5em; color:#000000; font-family:Muli, sans-serif; font-size:16px;">
                                                                            <li>Standard test strategy and templates
                                                                            </li>
                                                                            <li>Predefined regression coverage</li>
                                                                            <li>Environment and data readiness support
                                                                            </li>
                                                                        </ul>
                                                                        <h3
                                                                            style="font-size:18px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.6em; margin-bottom:0.6em;">
                                                                            Reusable Test Libraries</h3>
                                                                        <ul
                                                                            style="margin-bottom:1em; padding-left:1.5em; color:#000000; font-family:Muli, sans-serif; font-size:16px;">
                                                                            <li>Library of standard manual test suites
                                                                            </li>
                                                                            <li>Reusable automation test cases</li>
                                                                            <li>Reusable integration testing framework
                                                                            </li>
                                                                        </ul>
                                                                        <p style="margin-bottom:1em;">This asset-based
                                                                            approach ensures <strong>consistent quality,
                                                                                faster execution, and lower cost of
                                                                                testing</strong> over time.</p>
                                                                        <h2
                                                                            style="font-size:22px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.8em; margin-bottom:0.8em;">
                                                                            Test Automation for Dynamics 365 Operations
                                                                        </h2>
                                                                        <p style="margin-bottom:0.8em;">Our TaaS
                                                                            offering incorporates <strong>automation-led
                                                                                regression and validation</strong> to
                                                                            support frequent releases and continuous
                                                                            change.</p>
                                                                        <ul
                                                                            style="margin-bottom:1em; padding-left:1.5em; color:#000000; font-family:Muli, sans-serif; font-size:16px;">
                                                                            <li>Automation coverage for critical
                                                                                business processes</li>
                                                                            <li>Reusable scripts aligned with standard
                                                                                test scenarios</li>
                                                                            <li>Reduced manual effort and faster release
                                                                                cycles</li>
                                                                            <li>Improved repeatability and accuracy of
                                                                                testing</li>
                                                                        </ul>
                                                                        <p style="margin-bottom:1em;">Automation is
                                                                            applied pragmatically&mdash;focused on
                                                                            <strong>high-impact, high-risk, and
                                                                                repeatable scenarios</strong>.</p>
                                                                        <h2
                                                                            style="font-size:22px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.8em; margin-bottom:0.8em;">
                                                                            Application Monitoring &amp; Operational
                                                                            Insights</h2>
                                                                        <p style="margin-bottom:0.8em;">Beyond testing,
                                                                            we extend assurance into the <strong>run
                                                                                phase</strong> with application
                                                                            monitoring support.</p>
                                                                        <h3
                                                                            style="font-size:18px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.6em; margin-bottom:0.6em;">
                                                                            What We Monitor</h3>
                                                                        <ul
                                                                            style="margin-bottom:1em; padding-left:1.5em; color:#000000; font-family:Muli, sans-serif; font-size:16px;">
                                                                            <li>Application performance and system
                                                                                health</li>
                                                                            <li>Batch processing and scheduling</li>
                                                                            <li>Data management framework execution</li>
                                                                            <li>Error trends and incident patterns</li>
                                                                        </ul>
                                                                        <h3
                                                                            style="font-size:18px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.6em; margin-bottom:0.6em;">
                                                                            Value Delivered</h3>
                                                                        <ul
                                                                            style="margin-bottom:1em; padding-left:1.5em; color:#000000; font-family:Muli, sans-serif; font-size:16px;">
                                                                            <li>Proactive visibility into application
                                                                                behavior</li>
                                                                            <li>Faster root-cause analysis of incidents
                                                                            </li>
                                                                            <li>Improved operational stability and
                                                                                reliability</li>
                                                                        </ul>
                                                                        <h2
                                                                            style="font-size:22px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.8em; margin-bottom:0.8em;">
                                                                            Governance, Metrics &amp; Reporting</h2>
                                                                        <p style="margin-bottom:0.8em;">Our TaaS
                                                                            engagement is governed through structured
                                                                            reporting and measurable outcomes:</p>
                                                                        <ul
                                                                            style="margin-bottom:1em; padding-left:1.5em; color:#000000; font-family:Muli, sans-serif; font-size:16px;">
                                                                            <li>Test execution and defect dashboards
                                                                            </li>
                                                                            <li>Release readiness and risk assessments
                                                                            </li>
                                                                            <li>Defect trends and root-cause analysis
                                                                            </li>
                                                                            <li>Stakeholder reporting and governance
                                                                                cadence</li>
                                                                        </ul>
                                                                        <p style="margin-bottom:1em;">This ensures
                                                                            <strong>predictability, transparency, and
                                                                                audit-ready testing outcomes</strong>.
                                                                        </p>
                                                                        <h2
                                                                            style="font-size:22px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.8em; margin-bottom:0.8em;">
                                                                            Business Value of Our Dynamics 365 TaaS</h2>
                                                                        <p style="margin-bottom:1em;">Organizations
                                                                            leveraging our Testing-as-a-Service model
                                                                            for Dynamics 365 Operations achieve:</p>
                                                                        <ul
                                                                            style="margin-bottom:1em; padding-left:1.5em; color:#000000; font-family:Muli, sans-serif; font-size:16px;">
                                                                            <li>Faster time-to-market for releases</li>
                                                                            <li>Reduced production defects and defect
                                                                                leakage</li>
                                                                            <li>Improved test coverage without linear
                                                                                cost increase</li>
                                                                            <li>Lower cost of quality</li>
                                                                            <li>Higher productivity and efficiency
                                                                                year-on-year</li>
                                                                        </ul>
                                                                        <h2
                                                                            style="font-size:22px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.8em; margin-bottom:0.8em;">
                                                                            Delivery Model</h2>
                                                                        <ul
                                                                            style="margin-bottom:1em; padding-left:1.5em; color:#000000; font-family:Muli, sans-serif; font-size:16px;">
                                                                            <li>Global delivery with structured
                                                                                governance</li>
                                                                            <li>Scalable capacity based on release
                                                                                demand</li>
                                                                            <li>Dedicated test leadership and domain
                                                                                expertise</li>
                                                                            <li>Seamless collaboration with client and
                                                                                SI teams</li>
                                                                        </ul>
                                                                        <h2
                                                                            style="font-size:22px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.8em; margin-bottom:0.8em;">
                                                                            When to Choose Our TaaS for Dynamics 365
                                                                            Operations</h2>
                                                                        <ul
                                                                            style="margin-bottom:1em; padding-left:1.5em; color:#000000; font-family:Muli, sans-serif; font-size:16px;">
                                                                            <li>Run frequent Dynamics 365 Operations
                                                                                releases</li>
                                                                            <li>Struggle with regression effort and
                                                                                release confidence</li>
                                                                            <li>Want predictable testing costs and
                                                                                outcomes</li>
                                                                            <li>Need structured testing without building
                                                                                large in-house teams</li>
                                                                            <li>Require continuous assurance across
                                                                                change and run phases</li>
                                                                        </ul>
                                                                        <h2
                                                                            style="font-size:22px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:0.8em; margin-bottom:0.8em;">
                                                                            Get Started</h2>
                                                                        <p style="margin-bottom:1em;">Whether you are
                                                                            planning a major release, managing
                                                                            continuous enhancements, or stabilizing
